graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0 RHOAI]

    %% External Platform Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|orchestration<br/>REQUIRED| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.25+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|TLS certs<br/>OPTIONAL| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+]
    KubeRay -.->|monitoring<br/>OPTIONAL| Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling<br/>OPTIONAL| Volcano[Volcano 1.6+]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance<br/>OPTIONAL| Redis[External Redis 6.x]

    %% Service Mesh (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|mTLS + traffic<br/>OPTIONAL| Istio[Service Mesh - Istio]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusODH[Prometheus<br/>ODH/RHOAI]
    KubeRay -.->|UI integration<br/>OPTIONAL| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    KubeRay -.->|service mesh<br/>OPTIONAL| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>ODH/RHOAI]

    %% External Services
    KubeRay -->|model storage<br/>checkpointing| S3[S3 / Object Storage]
    KubeRay -->|container images| Registry[Container Registry]

    %% Ray Cluster Dependencies (Created by KubeRay)
    KubeRay -->|manages| RayCluster[Ray Cluster]
    RayCluster -->|coordinates via| GCS[Ray GCS<br/>Global Control Store]
    RayCluster -->|serves models| RayServe[Ray Serve]
    RayCluster -->|batch jobs| RayJob[Ray Job]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| KubeRay
    ServiceMesh -.->|secures| RayCluster

    %% API Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|REST API<br/>6443/TCP| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    PrometheusODH -->|scrapes<br/>8080/TCP| KubeRay

